President Kenyatta's big four agenda stands on 4 key pillars, one of which is manufacturing. Buy Kenya, build Kenya has been a constant call for years. With the world grappling with COVID?19, the inflow of goods has been limited ? forcing us to look inward for various essential products. Ktn news' maalika kazia takes a look at the  current of state manufacturing and trade in the country as well as expectations ahead of the national budget